&lt;li&gt;Thrive in a fast-paced, high-volume environment—making 80+ outbound calls each day is just part of your rhythm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excel at managing multiple prospects across different stages of the sales cycle through a mix of calls, emails, texts, and social outreach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take initiative in learning and mastering BILL’s product suite and value proposition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently meet—and aim to exceed—weekly and monthly KPIs including call volume (80+ outbound calls per day), meetings booked, opportunities created, and deals influenced&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embrace a collaborative, team-first culture where daily huddles are an opportunity to align on goals and celebrate wins&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are resilient, adaptable, and a strong communicator—especially when navigating objections and turning challenges into opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
