&lt;li&gt;Design and implement end-to-end solutions for customer acquisition and monitoring domains, including policies, rule strategies, ML/AI model strategies, product requirements, governance structures, and decision management frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct investments in risk management systems, including in-product and back-end controls, rule-based and predictive risk models, and third-party risk assessment tools.&lt;/li&gt;
